PART 3 — NEW ANALYTICS ARCHITECTURE
3.1 Extended Intent Flow
User types message in Analytics page
        ↓
Module selector (frontend dropdown): RMS / HRMS / MRR
        ↓
chat_controller receives: message + collection_context (e.g., "RMS_ANALYTICS")
        ↓
Controller sees collection_context ends with "_ANALYTICS"
        ↓
Invokes: get_analytics_graph() with collection_context passed in state
        ↓
Analytics graph runs (see section 3.3)
        ↓
Returns: chart / table / text via SSE

The existing module intent classifier is NOT used for analytics. The module is determined by the frontend dropdown selection, not LLM guessing. This removes all ambiguity.

